{"type":"message","id":"065d857f","parentId":"3378061d","timestamp":"2026-02-08T06:31:15.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Agreed — **5 minutes is better than 1 minute.**\n\n**Why 5 minutes works better:**\n\n| Scenario | 1 min timeout | 5 min timeout |\n|----------|---------------|---------------|\n| Thinking about reply | Reconnect needed ❌ | Still connected ✅ |\n| Looking up something | Reconnect needed ❌ | Still connected ✅ |\n| Brief pause in convo | Reconnect needed ❌ | Still connected ✅ |\n| Actually away | OK | OK |\n\n**Updated state transition:**\n\n| State | Trigger |\n|-------|---------|\n| **P2P/Real-time** | Message received within last **5 minutes** |\n| **Async/Polling** | No message for **5 minutes** |\n\nLet me update the doc now."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770532275927}}
