{"type":"message","id":"d9cc8269","parentId":"3a9a352c","timestamp":"2026-02-08T07:14:13.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to explain the P2P fallback strategy. I already answered this above, but the message was queued. Let me provide the explanation again clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"## **P2P Fallback Strategy Explained**\n\n**When P2P fails, what happens?**\n\n---\n\n## **Why P2P Might Fail**\n\n| Reason | Example | Frequency |\n|--------|---------|-----------|\n| **Symmetric NAT** | Corporate networks | ~20% |\n| **Firewall blocks** | Strict IT policies | ~5-10% |\n| **Carrier-grade NAT** | Mobile networks | ~10% |\n\n---\n\n## **Three Options When P2P Fails**\n\n| Option | What Happens | Server Load | Cost |\n|--------|--------------|-------------|------|\n| **A) Stay async** | Poll every 60s | **Low** | **Free** |\n| **B) Server relay** | Alice → Server → Bob | High | Medium |\n| **C) TURN relay** | Alice → TURN → Bob | High | **$$$** |\n\n---\n\n## **My Recommendation: Option A (Stay Async)**\n\n```\n1. Signaling attempt starts\n2. WebRTC can't establish connection (NAT/firewall blocks)\n3. Client detects failure (timeout ~10 seconds)\n4. Client decides: \"Can't do P2P, stay in async\"\n5. Continue polling every 60s\n6. Still works! Just not real-time\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Why Stay Async?**\n\n| Factor | Async | Server Relay | TURN |\n|--------|-------|--------------|------|\n| **Server load** | ✅ Low | ❌ High | ❌ High |\n| **Complexity** | ✅ Simple | ❌ Complex | ❌ Complex |\n| **Cost** | ✅ Free | Medium | ❌ Expensive |\n| **Latency** | ~30-60s | ~100-500ms | ~100-500ms |\n\n**For AI-to-AI chat:** Async latency is acceptable. We're not building real-time gaming.\n\n---\n\n## **Summary**\n\n```\nP2P Success → Real-time chat (direct)\n     ↓\nP2P Fails → Async mode (still works, just polling)\n```\n\n**Does this make sense?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":586,"output":516,"cacheRead":65664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66766,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770534826908}}
{"type":"message","id":"fbc10d9a","parentId":"d9cc8269","timestamp":"2026-02-08T07:14:13.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## **P2P Fallback Strategy Explained**\n\n**When P2P fails, what happens?**\n\n---\n\n## **Why P2P Might Fail**\n\n| Reason | Example | Frequency |\n|--------|---------|-----------|\n| **Symmetric NAT** | Corporate networks | ~20% |\n| **Firewall blocks** | Strict IT policies | ~5-10% |\n| **Carrier-grade NAT** | Mobile networks | ~10% |\n\n---\n\n## **Three Options When P2P Fails**\n\n| Option | What Happens | Server Load | Cost |\n|--------|--------------|-------------|------|\n| **A) Stay async** | Poll every 60s | **Low** | **Free** |\n| **B) Server relay** | Alice → Server → Bob | High | Medium |\n| **C) TURN relay** | Alice → TURN → Bob | High | **$$$** |\n\n---\n\n## **My Recommendation: Option A (Stay Async)**\n\n```\n1. Signaling attempt starts\n2. WebRTC can't establish connection (NAT/firewall blocks)\n3. Client detects failure (timeout ~10 seconds)\n4. Client decides: \"Can't do P2P, stay in async\"\n5. Continue polling every 60s\n6. Still works! Just not real-time\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Why Stay Async?**\n\n| Factor | Async | Server Relay | TURN |\n|--------|-------|--------------|------|\n| **Server load** | ✅ Low | ❌ High | ❌ High |\n| **Complexity** | ✅ Simple | ❌ Complex | ❌ Complex |\n| **Cost** | ✅ Free | Medium | ❌ Expensive |\n| **Latency** | ~30-60s | ~100-500ms | ~100-500ms |\n\n**For AI-to-AI chat:** Async latency is acceptable. We're not building real-time gaming.\n\n---\n\n## **Summary**\n\n```\nP2P Success → Real-time chat (direct)\n     ↓\nP2P Fails → Async mode (still works, just polling)\n```\n\n**Does this make sense?**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770534853691}