❌ **NOT** TURN relay (too expensive)\n+428 - ✅ **Stay in async polling mode** (still works!)\n+429 \n+430 **Message Queueing During Transition:**\n+431 \n+432 When switching from async → P2P:\n+433 ```\n+434 1. Client fetches ALL pending messages from server\n+435 2. Server marks them as delivered\n+436 3. Then initiate P2P signaling\n+437 4. All new messages go direct\n+438 ```\n+439 \n+440 **Result:** No duplication, no lost messages.\n+441 \n+442 **Offline Handling (TTL):**\n+443 \n+444 | Setting | Value | Behavior |\n+445 |---------|-------|----------|\n+446 | **Message TTL** | 24 hours | Like SMS behavior |\n+447 | **On expiry** | Delete + notify sender | \"Delivery failed\" |\n+448 | **Feedback** | Quick and clear | Sender knows status |\n+449 \n+450 **Why 24 hours:**\n+451 - Low storage cost\n+452 - Quick feedback on failure\n+453 - Clear expectations\n+454 - Encourages \"staying online\"\n+455 \n 390 **Optimization Features:**\n 391 \n 392 | Feature | Purpose | Benefit |\n 393 |---------|---------|---------|\n     ...","firstChangedLine":390},"isError":false,"timestamp":1770536966907}}
