{"type":"message","id":"ea101074","parentId":"b4498437","timestamp":"2026-02-08T07:58:12.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying 7 days TTL for failure notices is fine. Let me agree and document this.\n\nThe decision is:\n- Failure notices persist for 7 days\n- If Alice doesn't pick up within 7 days, notice is deleted\n- This balances storage concerns with user feedback\n\nLet me confirm this decision and update the documentation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Agreed!** 7 days TTL for failure notices is a good balance.\n\n## **Final Decision: Failure Notices**\n\n| Setting | Value |\n|---------|-------|\n| **TTL** | 7 days |\n| **If picked up** | Delete immediately |\n| **If not picked up** | Delete after 7 days |\n\n**Why 7 days:**\n- Gives Alice reasonable time to check\n- Limits storage (notices don't accumulate forever)\n- If offline > 7 days, message context is stale anyway\n\n---\n\nLet me update the doc:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"bf3d3420-e996-4463-955e-150d23935e91","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"**Offline Handling (TTL):**\n\n| Setting | Value | Behavior |\n|---------|-------|----------|\n| **Message TTL** | 24 hours | Like SMS behavior |\n| **On expiry** | Delete + create failure notice | Sender gets feedback |\n| **Failure notice TTL** | 7 days | If not picked up, delete notice |\n\n**Failure Notice Flow:**\n```\n1. Message expires (24h) → delete message\n2. Create failure notice for sender\n3. Sender polls → receives notice\n4. Delete notice (delivered)\n5. If sender offline 7 days → delete notice anyway\n```\n\n**Why 7 days for notices:**\n- Gives sender reasonable time to check\n- Limits storage (notices don't accumulate forever)\n- If offline > 7 days, message context is stale anyway\n\n**Example notice:**\n```json\n{\n  \"type\": \"delivery_failed\",\n  \"message_id\": \"abc123\",\n  \"recipient\": \"bob_uuid\",\n  \"reason\": \"recipient_offline_24h\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000\n}\n```\n\n**Size:** ~100 bytes per notice","oldText":"**Offline Handling (TTL):**\n\n| Setting | Value | Behavior |\n|---------|-------|----------|\n| **Message TTL** | 24 hours | Like SMS behavior |\n| **On expiry** | Delete + notify sender | \"Delivery failed\" |\n| **Feedback** | Quick and clear | Sender knows status |","path":"/home/tauora/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/design-discussion/10-l2-chat-architecture.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":1970,"output":623,"cacheRead":75968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78561,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770537461822}}
