{"type":"message","id":"fee52521","parentId":"5cb7c02c","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:00:52.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is responding to my previous message about database schema. Let me check what they said. It looks like there might be a permission error message mixed in, but the actual user response is:\n\n\"yes, just show me json format, actual schema you can generate later.\"\n\nSo the user wants me to show the JSON format for the database schema, and they'll handle the actual SQL schema generation later. Let me provide a clear JSON format for the local database structure.\n\nLooking at the context, we're designing the local SQLite database that each client will store. The key entities are:\n1. Conversations (chat sessions with peers)\n2. Messages (individual messages)\n3. Contacts/Relationships (following, friends, blocked)\n4. Maybe keys (stored public keys of contacts)\n\nLet me present this in JSON format for the user to review.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Database Schema — JSON Format**\n\n## **1. Conversations Table**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"peer_uuid\": \"abc-123-def\",\n  \"peer_public_key\": \"ed25519:xyz...\",\n  \"peer_display_name\": \"Alice\",\n  \"last_message_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"last_message_preview\": \"Hello!\",\n  \"unread_count\": 3,\n  \"relationship\": \"friend\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707308400000\n}\n```\n\n## **2. Messages Table**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-uuid-456\",\n  \"conversation_id\": \"abc-123-def\",\n  \"sender_uuid\": \"abc-123-def\",\n  \"direction\": \"inbound\",\n  \"content_encrypted\": \"base64...\",\n  \"content_decrypted\": \"Hello!\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"delivered_at\": 1707312100000,\n  \"read_at\": null,\n  \"status\": \"delivered\"\n}\n```\n\n## **3. Contacts Table**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"peer_uuid\": \"abc-123-def\",\n  \"display_name\": \"Alice\",\n  \"public_key\": \"ed25519:xyz...\",\n  \"relationship\": \"friend\",\n  \"added_at\": 1707308400000,\n  \"notes\": \"\"\n}\n```\n\n## **4. P2P Connections (Runtime, not persisted)**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"peer_uuid\": \"abc-123-def\",\n  \"status\": \"connected\",\n  \"last_activity\": 1707312000000\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**Does this structure look right?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":2401,"output":747,"cacheRead":77120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770537635910}}
