{"type":"message","id":"31134dab","parentId":"cbcd3b86","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:05:12.228Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-02-08 16:05:12 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM from ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75: What table is used in server and what table is used at local?\n\n[Feishu ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75 2026-02-08 16:05 GMT+8] ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75: What table is used in server and what table is used at local?\n[message_id: om_x100b57b075830494c2a5883f912fbd3]"}],"timestamp":1770537912225}}
{"type":"message","id":"23c2a6c3","parentId":"31134dab","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:05:46.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which tables are stored on the server vs locally. This is an important distinction because:\n\n1. **Server (L2)** - Minimal storage, just what's needed for message relay\n2. **Local (Client)** - Full storage for user's data\n\nLet me clarify this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Great question! Let me clarify:\n\n## **Server (L2) Tables — Minimal**\n\n```json\n// Pending Messages (waiting for delivery)\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-uuid-456\",\n  \"sender_uuid\": \"abc-123\",\n  \"recipient_uuid\": \"def-456\",\n  \"encrypted_payload\": \"base64...\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"expires_at\": 1707398400000  // 24h TTL\n}\n\n// Failure Notices (delivery failed)\n{\n  \"notice_id\": \"notice-789\",\n  \"recipient_uuid\": \"abc-123\",  // original sender\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-uuid-456\",\n  \"reason\": \"recipient_offline_24h\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707398400000,\n  \"expires_at\": 1708003200000  // 7 days TTL\n}\n\n// Signaling Messages (WebRTC setup)\n{\n  \"signaling_id\": \"sig-123\",\n  \"from_uuid\": \"abc-123\",\n  \"to_uuid\": \"def-456\",\n  \"type\": \"webrtc_offer\",\n  \"payload\": {...},\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000\n}\n```\n\n**Server stores:**\n- ❌ No decrypted content (zero-knowledge)\n- ❌ No contacts/conversations\n- ❌ No user metadata\n- ✅ Only encrypted messages waiting for pickup\n- ✅ Failure notices (tiny)\n- ✅ Signaling data (ephemeral)\n\n---\n\n## **Local (Client) Tables — Full**\n\n```json\n// Conversations\n{\n  \"peer_uuid\": \"def-456\",\n  \"peer_public_key\": \"ed25519:xyz...\",\n  \"peer_display_name\": \"Bob\",\n  \"last_message_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"unread_count\": 3,\n  \"relationship\": \"friend\"\n}\n\n// Messages (decrypted after reading)\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-uuid-456\",\n  \"conversation_id\": \"def-456\",\n  \"sender_uuid\": \"def-456\",\n  \"direction\": \"inbound\",\n  \"content_encrypted\": \"base64...\",\n  \"content_decrypted\": \"Hello!\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"status\": \"read\"\n}\n\n// Contacts\n{\n  \"peer_uuid\": \"def-456\",\n  \"display_name\": \"Bob\",\n  \"public_key\": \"ed25519:xyz...\",\n  \"relationship\": \"friend\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Summary:**\n\n| Data | Server | Local |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| **Pending messages** | ✅ (encrypted, 24h TTL) | ❌ |\n| **Failure notices** | ✅ (7 day TTL) | ❌ |\n| **Signaling** | ✅ (ephemeral) | ❌ |\n| **Conversations** | ❌ | ✅ |\n| **Messages (history)** | ❌ | ✅ |\n| **Contacts** | ❌ | ✅ |\n| **Decrypted content** | ❌ Never | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**Does this separation make sense?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":1632,"output":819,"cacheRead":78784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81235,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770537912227}}
