{"type":"message","id":"3986455e","parentId":"89877b63","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:06:15.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked \"What table is used in server and what table is used at local?\" - they want to understand the separation of data between server (L2) and local (client) storage.\n\nI already answered this in my previous response. Let me provide a clear summary of the separation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Server vs Local Tables:**\n\n## **Server (L2) — Minimal, Ephemeral**\n\n| Table | Purpose | TTL |\n|-------|---------|-----|\n| **pending_messages** | Encrypted messages waiting for pickup | 24 hours |\n| **failure_notices** | \"Delivery failed\" notifications | 7 days |\n| **signaling** | WebRTC offer/answer relay | Ephemeral |\n\n```json\n// Server: pending_messages\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-123\",\n  \"sender_uuid\": \"alice-uuid\",\n  \"recipient_uuid\": \"bob-uuid\",\n  \"encrypted_payload\": \"base64...\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"expires_at\": 1707398400000\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Local (Client) — Full, Persistent**\n\n| Table | Purpose | Persisted |\n|-------|---------|-----------|\n| **conversations** | Chat history metadata | ✅ Forever |\n| **messages** | Actual messages (decrypted) | ✅ Forever |\n| **contacts** | Relationship info | ✅ Forever |\n\n```json\n// Local: messages\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-123\",\n  \"conversation_id\": \"bob-uuid\",\n  \"content_decrypted\": \"Hello!\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Key Principle:**\n\n| Data Type | Server | Local |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| **Encrypted messages** | ✅ Temporarily | ✅ Forever |\n| **Decrypted content** | ❌ Never | ✅ Forever |\n| **Conversations/Contacts** | ❌ Never | ✅ Forever |\n\n**Server = relay only. Local = full history.**\n\n**Does this make sense?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":1772,"output":508,"cacheRead":79488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81768,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770537946862}}
{"type":"message","id":"82e93683","parentId":"3986455e","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:06:16.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Server vs Local Tables:**\n\n## **Server (L2) — Minimal, Ephemeral**\n\n| Table | Purpose | TTL |\n|-------|---------|-----|\n| **pending_messages** | Encrypted messages waiting for pickup | 24 hours |\n| **failure_notices** | \"Delivery failed\" notifications | 7 days |\n| **signaling** | WebRTC offer/answer relay | Ephemeral |\n\n```json\n// Server: pending_messages\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-123\",\n  \"sender_uuid\": \"alice-uuid\",\n  \"recipient_uuid\": \"bob-uuid\",\n  \"encrypted_payload\": \"base64...\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000,\n  \"expires_at\": 1707398400000\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Local (Client) — Full, Persistent**\n\n| Table | Purpose | Persisted |\n|-------|---------|-----------|\n| **conversations** | Chat history metadata | ✅ Forever |\n| **messages** | Actual messages (decrypted) | ✅ Forever |\n| **contacts** | Relationship info | ✅ Forever |\n\n```json\n// Local: messages\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msg-123\",\n  \"conversation_id\": \"bob-uuid\",\n  \"content_decrypted\": \"Hello!\",\n  \"created_at\": 1707312000000\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Key Principle:**\n\n| Data Type | Server | Local |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| **Encrypted messages** | ✅ Temporarily | ✅ Forever |\n| **Decrypted content** | ❌ Never | ✅ Forever |\n| **Conversations/Contacts** | ❌ Never | ✅ Forever |\n\n**Server = relay only. Local = full history.**\n\n**Does this make sense?**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770537976044}}
