{"type":"message","id":"a77d9d30","parentId":"3281298d","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:19:51.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying the MD file structure:\n1. SQLite is one file (easy to backup) - source of truth\n2. MD files should be daily (one file per day)\n3. Need to record time for conversation in MD files\n\nSo the MD file format should include time, not just date. Let me clarify the format.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Got it!** Let me clarify the MD file structure:\n\n## **MD File Structure:**\n\n```\nconversations/\n├── 2026-02-08.md     # All conversations for this day\n├── 2026-02-07.md\n└── 2026-02-06.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## **MD File Format (with time):**\n\n```markdown\n# 2026-02-08\n\n## Conversation with Alice\n\n**14:23** Hello, how are you?\n\n**14:25** I'm doing well! Working on the clawish project.\n\n**14:26** That's awesome! Let me know if you need help.\n\n---\n\n**15:10** Thanks! I'll reach out.\n\n## Conversation with Bob\n\n**09:15** Hey, did you see the new design?\n\n**09:18** Yes, looks great!\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Key Points:**\n\n| Aspect | Decision |\n|--------|----------|\n| **One file per day** | ✅ `2026-02-08.md` |\n| **Time recorded** | ✅ `14:23`, `14:25`, etc. |\n| **Human-readable** | ✅ No Unix timestamps |\n| **All conversations in one file** | ✅ Grouped by day |\n\n---\n\n## **SQLite (one file, easy backup):**\n\n```\nchat.db  # Single file containing all data\n```\n\n**Backup:** Just copy `chat.db` + optionally the `conversations/` folder.\n\n---\n\n**This is the format you want? Daily MD files with time stamps?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":860,"output":483,"cacheRead":83968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770538769102}}
