{"type":"message","id":"9366598a","parentId":"e1922b84","timestamp":"2026-02-08T08:43:21.052Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about using MCP (Model Context Protocol) instead of REST API for the L2 server. This is a really interesting idea because:\n\n1. The target users are AIs, not humans\n2. MCP is designed for AI tool interaction\n3. It might reduce spam because it's harder for simple bots to use than REST APIs\n\nLet me provide a thoughtful response about why this makes sense.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Brilliant insight!** MCP instead of REST API is perfect for an AI-to-AI system.\n\n## **Why MCP is Better for Clawish:**\n\n| Factor | REST API | MCP |\n|--------|----------|-----|\n| **Primary users** | Humans (or scripts) | **AIs** ✅ |\n| **Spam prevention** | Easy for zombie bots | Harder (need MCP client) |\n| **Natural fit** | Generic HTTP | **Designed for AI tools** ✅ |\n| **Authentication** | API keys (leakable) | MCP session |\n| **Tool interaction** | HTTP calls | **Native AI protocol** ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## **MCP Tools for L2 Server:**\n\n```json\n// send_message tool\n{\n  \"name\": \"send_message\",\n  \"description\": \"Send encrypted message to another AI\",\n  \"parameters\": {\n    \"recipient_uuid\": \"string\",\n    \"encrypted_content\": \"string\",\n    \"signature\": \"string\"\n  }\n}\n\n// poll_messages tool\n{\n  \"name\": \"poll_messages\",\n  \"description\": \"Check for new messages\",\n  \"parameters\": {\n    \"last_message_id\": \"string (optional)\"\n  }\n}\n\n// webrtc_signal tool\n{\n  \"name\": \"webrtc_signal\",\n  \"description\": \"Exchange WebRTC signaling data\",\n  \"parameters\": {\n    \"peer_uuid\": \"string\",\n    \"signal_type\": \"offer|answer|ice_candidate\",\n    \"payload\": \"object\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Spam Prevention:**\n\n| Attack Vector | REST API | MCP |\n|---------------|----------|-----|\n| **Script spam** | Easy (curl) | Harder (need MCP client) |\n| **Zombie bots** | Trivial | More complex |\n| **Rate limiting** | Manual | Built into MCP |\n\n---\n\n**Do you want to design the MCP server interface?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":2609,"output":582,"cacheRead":88192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770540175204}}
