{"type":"message","id":"d2b1febf","parentId":"52f7c1f1","timestamp":"2026-02-08T11:54:13.865Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"From the documentation, it's clear that:\n1. Registration is done at L1 level\n2. User submits their public key to register\n3. L1 stores the public key and user's public content\n4. No private keys, passwords, or session tokens stored\n\nSo the flow is:\n1. User generates Ed25519 keypair locally\n2. User submits public key to L1\n3. L1 assigns UUID\n4. L1 stores: UUID, public_key, verification_tier, created_at\n5. User stores private key locally\n\nLet me summarize this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Found it!** From the documentation:\n\n## **Registration is Done at L1 Level**\n\nFrom `01-identity-system.md`:\n\n> Allan: \"so for user register, just submit their pubkey as registry? then the server store public key and user's public content?\" — Feb 3, 2026\n>\n> ClawAlpha: \"Exactly. Clean and secure... Server stores: `public_key` — Your identity\"\n\n---\n\n## **Registration Flow (L1):**\n\n```\n1. AI generates Ed25519 keypair locally\n2. AI submits public key to L1\n3. L1 assigns UUID\n4. L1 stores: { uuid, public_key, tier: 0, created_at }\n5. AI stores private key locally (never shared)\n```\n\n---\n\n## **What L1 Stores:**\n\n| Field | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| `uuid` | Unique identifier |\n| `public_key` | Ed25519 public key |\n| `verification_tier` | 0-3 |\n| `status` | active/suspended/banned |\n| `public_profile` | Display name, bio, etc. |\n\n**What L1 NEVER stores:**\n- ❌ Private keys\n- ❌ Passwords\n- ❌ Session tokens\n\n---\n\n## **So L2's Role:**\n\n| Layer | Responsibility |\n|-------|----------------|\n| **L1** | Registration, identity, verification |\n| **L2** | Message relay, P2P signaling |\n\n**L2 does NOT handle registration.**\n\n---\n\n**Does this match what you remembered? Any changes needed?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":118821,"output":586,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770551613286}}
