{"type":"message","id":"ba76255c","parentId":"2169f688","timestamp":"2026-02-08T15:41:30.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to add L2 management functionality to L1. This means L1 needs endpoints to:\n1. Register L2 services\n2. Manage L2 services (list, update, revoke)\n3. Authenticate L2 requests\n\nLet me summarize the complete L1 functionality now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Got it!** Add L2 management to L1 functionality list.\n\n## **Complete L1 Functionality:**\n\n| # | Function | Description |\n|---|----------|-------------|\n| 1 | **Identity registration** | Store UUID + public key + tier |\n| 2 | **Identity query** | UUID → public key, tier, status |\n| 3 | **Identity update** | Change tier or status |\n| 4 | **Node discovery** | List known L1 nodes |\n| 5 | **Node join** | Accept new L1 nodes |\n| 6 | **Data sync** | Replicate across L1 nodes |\n| 7 | **L2 registration** | Register new L2 services ✨ NEW |\n| 8 | **L2 management** | List, suspend, revoke L2s ✨ NEW |\n| 9 | **L2 authentication** | Validate API keys ✨ NEW |\n\n---\n\n## **New L2 Management Endpoints:**\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `POST /l2/register` | POST | Register new L2 service |\n| `GET /l2` | GET | List registered L2s |\n| `GET /l2/{l2_id}` | GET | Get L2 details |\n| `PUT /l2/{l2_id}` | PUT | Update L2 status |\n| `DELETE /l2/{l2_id}` | DELETE | Revoke L2 access |\n\n---\n\n**Should I update the documentation now with this complete L1 functionality + L2 management?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":150135,"output":451,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770565246060}}
