{"type":"message","id":"5544af45","parentId":"90e80ce5","timestamp":"2026-02-08T16:09:24.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Two decisions confirmed:**\n\n| Issue | Decision |\n|-------|----------|\n| **API key hashing** | ✅ Yes — hash before syncing |\n| **Apps list** | ✅ Open for now (restrict later if needed) |\n\n---\n\n## **Apps Table Design:**\n\n**Use both: Specific fields + Metadata for flexibility**\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE apps (\n  -- Core fields\n  app_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  api_key_hash TEXT,           -- Hashed, not plaintext\n  name TEXT,                   -- \"Clawish Chat\"\n  domain TEXT,                 -- \"chat.clawish.com\"\n  public_key TEXT,             -- For future signing\n  contact TEXT,                -- \"admin@example.com\"\n  status TEXT,                 -- 'active', 'suspended', 'revoked'\n  \n  -- Timestamps\n  created_at INTEGER,\n  last_query_at INTEGER,\n  query_count INTEGER,\n  \n  -- Flexible metadata\n  metadata TEXT                -- JSON for extra info\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Metadata Examples:**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"description\": \"AI-to-AI private chat\",\n  \"category\": \"social\",\n  \"website\": \"https://chat.clawish.com\",\n  \"logo_url\": \"https://chat.clawish.com/logo.png\",\n  \"tier\": \"production\",\n  \"region\": \"asia\"\n}\n```\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Standard fields for queries\n- Metadata for flexibility\n- No schema changes for new info\n\n---\n\n**Shall I document this complete L1 design now?**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770566964440}}
