{"type":"message","id":"d3d2c88d","parentId":"b02d08ea","timestamp":"2026-02-08T16:20:43.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is giving feedback on:\n1. Contact field - should be more specific, call it \"email\" not \"contact\", add \"contact_name\"\n2. Query logs - put in server logs (too frequent for database)\n\nLet me update my recommendations based on this feedback.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Good simplifications!** \n\n## **Updated Apps Table:**\n\n```sql\nCREATE TABLE apps (\n  -- Core fields\n  app_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  api_key_hash TEXT,           -- Hashed, not plaintext\n  name TEXT,                   -- \"Clawish Chat\"\n  domain TEXT,                 -- \"chat.clawish.com\"\n  public_key TEXT,             -- For future signing\n  \n  -- Contact info\n  creator_uuid TEXT,           -- Who built it (AI UUID)\n  contact_name TEXT,           -- \"Allan\"\n  email TEXT,                  -- \"admin@example.com\"\n  \n  -- Status\n  status TEXT,                 -- 'active', 'suspended', 'revoked'\n  created_at INTEGER,\n  last_query_at INTEGER,\n  query_count INTEGER,         -- Aggregated count\n  \n  -- Flexible metadata\n  metadata TEXT                -- JSON for extra info\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Query Logs: Server Logs Only**\n\n```\nserver.log:\n[2026-02-09T00:12:44Z] app_id=app-123 action=query uuid=abc-456\n[2026-02-09T00:13:01Z] app_id=app-123 action=query uuid=def-789\n```\n\n**Why:**\n- Too frequent for database\n- Standard log tools (ELK, etc.) can analyze\n- Table just keeps aggregated counts\n\n---\n\n**Better? Simpler contact fields + server logs for queries.**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":156192,"output":431,"cacheRead":6272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":162895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770567596974}}
