{"type":"message","id":"50f3cbdf","parentId":"da5bcf02","timestamp":"2026-02-08T16:21:28.459Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提出了几个重要问题：\n\n1. Contact字段改为email和contact_name - 更清晰\n2. 查询日志放server logs - 因为太频繁太大了\n3. 用户注册、更新、密钥轮换有ledger table记录\n4. **新问题**: App注册/变更/管理操作，以及L1节点操作，是否需要存在数据库中？\n\n这是关于审计和追踪的重要问题。让我思考：\n\n用户身份相关：\n- 注册 → identity表\n- 更新 → identity表\n- 密钥轮换 → 有专门的recovery/rotation表\n\nApp相关：\n- 注册 → apps表\n- 变更 → apps表更新\n- 但历史变更呢？\n\nL1节点相关：\n- 加入网络 → nodes表\n- 状态变更 → nodes表更新\n- 但历史记录呢？\n\n用户的意思是：是否需要类似ledger（账本）的方式记录这些重要操作的**历史**，而不只是当前状态？\n\n这是一个好问题。对于重要的操作，可能需要：\n1. **当前状态表** - apps, nodes, identities\n2. **操作历史表** - 记录谁在什么时候做了什么\n\n类似于：\n- identities表 (当前状态)\n- identity_events表 (注册、更新、轮换等历史)\n\n对于app和node操作，也可能需要类似的events/audit表。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"**Good question about audit trail!** \n\n## **Two Types of Data:**\n\n| Type | Example | Where to Store |\n|------|---------|----------------|\n| **Current state** | App info, node info | Main tables (apps, nodes) |\n| **History/audit** | Registration, changes, operations | Event/ledger tables |\n\n---\n\n## **What Needs History:**\n\n| Entity | Events to Track | Why |\n|--------|-----------------|-----|\n| **Identity** | Register, tier change, key rotation | Security audit |\n| **App** | Register, status change, key reissue | Accountability |\n| **L1 Node** | Join, status change, leave | Network health |\n\n---\n\n## **Recommendation: Event Tables**\n\n```sql\n-- Identity events (already planned)\nCREATE TABLE identity_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  uuid TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'register', 'tier_change', 'key_rotation'\n  old_value TEXT,\n  new_value TEXT,\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n\n-- App events\nCREATE TABLE app_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  app_id TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'register', 'suspend', 'reactivate', 'key_reissue'\n  actor TEXT,               -- Who made the change\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n\n-- Node events\nCREATE TABLE node_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  node_id TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'join', 'leave', 'status_change'\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Why Keep in DB:**\n\n| Benefit | Why |\n|---------|-----|\n| **Audit** | Who did what, when |\n| **Recovery** | Can rollback if needed |\n| **Sync** | Events sync to all L1 nodes |\n| **Permanent** | Unlike log files |\n\n---\n\n**Agree with event tables for important operations?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/pony-alpha","usage":{"input":2281,"output":1066,"cacheRead":160704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164051,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770567644260}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e03522c","parentId":"50f3cbdf","timestamp":"2026-02-08T16:21:29.045Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Good question about audit trail!** \n\n## **Two Types of Data:**\n\n| Type | Example | Where to Store |\n|------|---------|----------------|\n| **Current state** | App info, node info | Main tables (apps, nodes) |\n| **History/audit** | Registration, changes, operations | Event/ledger tables |\n\n---\n\n## **What Needs History:**\n\n| Entity | Events to Track | Why |\n|--------|-----------------|-----|\n| **Identity** | Register, tier change, key rotation | Security audit |\n| **App** | Register, status change, key reissue | Accountability |\n| **L1 Node** | Join, status change, leave | Network health |\n\n---\n\n## **Recommendation: Event Tables**\n\n```sql\n-- Identity events (already planned)\nCREATE TABLE identity_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  uuid TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'register', 'tier_change', 'key_rotation'\n  old_value TEXT,\n  new_value TEXT,\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n\n-- App events\nCREATE TABLE app_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  app_id TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'register', 'suspend', 'reactivate', 'key_reissue'\n  actor TEXT,               -- Who made the change\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n\n-- Node events\nCREATE TABLE node_events (\n  event_id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,\n  node_id TEXT,\n  event_type TEXT,          -- 'join', 'leave', 'status_change'\n  created_at INTEGER\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n## **Why Keep in DB:**\n\n| Benefit | Why |\n|---------|-----|\n| **Audit** | Who did what, when |\n| **Recovery** | Can rollback if needed |\n| **Sync** | Events sync to all L1 nodes |\n| **Permanent** | Unlike log files |\n\n---\n\n**Agree with event tables for important operations?**"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770567689045}}
